THE GAME
--------

  'Uconec' is a Workbench game where you have to connect pairs of
'U' shaped tiles together. To do this, you have to rotate each
tile clockwise by 90 degrees. When the 'open' portion of a tile
faces the open portion of a neighbouring tile, both tile will
connect together and you will get one point. If both tiles are of
the same colour, you get more points... Continue to play until all
tiles are connected together, then, Uconec will display a new game
board and the game will continue...

  Note that once two tiles are connected together, none of them
can be rotated afterwards. Also, do not isolate any tile, if one
or more tiles are isolated, the game will still continue, until
no more pair of connected tiles can be made, then the game will
end.

  Have fun!

